channel.title: Helping People | .Jar File | If You Need To .Jar Read Me
channel.description:
Hello Guys, Just for those who need it, Ive got some free time for a hour or two so i thought id help the community beginers/noobs. If you are trying to .jar your delta or pi client but you just cant seem to do it pm me or comment below and i will take my time to help you and .jar it for you then send you it back.
If you dont need help, Then dont comment to cause trouble.
Thanks for reading.
